ln, by default, creates a hard link
		two types of links
			1 hard link
			2 soft link


			1)hard link 
					ranjit@ranjit-Vostro-1540:~/play$ ln demo.txt demo_ln.txt

					arch
							demo.txt->>>>>>    inode of file   <<<<<<<<<<<<<<<-----demo_ln.txt

			2)soft link
					ranjit@ranjit-Vostro-1540:~/play$ ln -s demo.txt demo_ln.txt

					arch
							demo_ln.txt->>>>>>>  demo.txt   ->>>>>> inode of file 
	